== 歷史 ==
數千年前，爆米花首次在被發現於[[印加帝國|印加帝國]]。它是玉米最古老的形式之一。

在[[大蕭條|大蕭條]]期間，爆米花因相對便宜，所以儘管其它業務不景气，爆米花業務却蓬勃發展，並成為了許多農民的主要收入來源<ref name="popcorn.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.popcorn.org/EncyclopediaPopcornica/WelcometoPopcornica/HistoryofPopcorn/tabid/106/Default.aspx|title=Encyclopedia Popcornica: Recent Popcorn History|accessdate=2013-05-15|archive-date=2013-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530041340/http://www.popcorn.org/EncyclopediaPopcornica/WelcometoPopcornica/HistoryofPopcorn/tabid/106/Default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[美國農業部|美國農業部]]統計，大部分[[玉米|玉米]]用於生產爆米花。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/usda/nass/Popc//1980s/1982/Popc-01-15-1982.pdf|title=United States Department of Agriculture - 1982 Popcorn Report|accessdate=2013-05-15|archive-date=2013-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116084040/http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/usda/nass/Popc//1980s/1982/Popc-01-15-1982.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/MannUsda/viewDocumentInfo.do?documentID=1685 |title=Reports for other years also available |accessdate=2013-05-15 |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116083740/http://usda.mannlib.cornell.edu/MannUsda/viewDocumentInfo.do?documentID=1685 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
